CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 6, 1962, pg. 10 reads: "Wed 50 Years - Mr. and Mrs. James Wooling of 3610 Colmar St., celebrated 50 golden years of married life at a reception last Saturday night. They have resided in same house since their marriage Oct. 2, 1912. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women, one on right wearing dark satin dress, and men, seated behind banquet table with ferns, in interior during fiftieth anniversary reception for Mr. and Mrs. James Wooling
